title: Sam Smith unveils waxwork at Madame Tussauds San Francisco [Photos]
text:
Tuesday, August 11, 2015 11:05 AM EDT Sam Smith unveils waxwork at Madame Tussauds 
Singer Sam Smith, right, licks the face of his wax figure at Madame Tussauds wax museum in San Francisco, Monday, Aug. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Jeff Chiu) AP 
Singer Sam Smith, right, takes a selfie next to his wax figure at Madame Tussauds wax museum in San Francisco, Monday, Aug. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Jeff Chiu) AP 
Singer Sam Smith, right, kisses the face of his wax figure while taking a selfie at Madame Tussauds wax museum in San Francisco, Monday, Aug. 10, 2015. (AP Photo/Jeff Chiu) AP 
Grammy award-winning singer Sam Smith, left, with his wax figure likeness during an unveiling ceremony at Madame Tussauds in San Francisco, Monday, Aug. 10, 2015. (Photo by Peter Barreras/Invision/AP) Peter Barreras/Invision/AP
